Smart Study Planner (Anime Edition)

A logic based study planner that helps students organize subjects, track progress, and prioritize exams efficiently, presented with a simple anime inspired interface.

Features
Add subjects with exam dates and difficulty level
Automatic priority based sorting
Countdown timer showing days left for exams
Progress tracker from 0 to 100 percent
Urgency alert for upcoming exams
Data persistence using Local Storage
Smooth UI animations
Logic Used

This project focuses on core data structures and logic building:

Sorting logic
Tasks are sorted based on:
Earliest exam date
Higher difficulty level
Priority handling
Subjects with closer deadlines and higher difficulty are shown first
Dynamic updates
Progress changes update the interface instantly
Tech Stack
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
Project Structure
Smart-Study-Planner
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── script.js
│── README.md
How to Run
Clone or download the repository
Open index.html in any browser
Start adding your study tasks
Use Case

This project helps students plan their studies, reduce last minute stress, and track their preparation effectively.

Future Improvements
Progress visualization using charts
